org.stormdev.mc.servermonitor.api.reports

Interface ServerEventReport

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    CombinedLagReport, CrashReport, ExceptionReport, HardCrashReport, LagReport, TimeoutCrashReport

    public interface ServerEventReport
    Represents a report about an event. This is used responders to perform their actions
